subject: Spark Meetup in Singapore
text:
Dear Sir/Madam,

We want to become an organiser of Singapore Meetup to promote the regional SPARK and big data
community in ASEAN area.

My name is Songtao, I am a big data consultant in Singapore and have great passion for Spark
technologies.



Thanks,
Songtao
